Item / technique / special-attack name data in pso_hud_items.txt,
pso_hud_techs.txt, and pso_hud_specials.txt is factual information derived
from Phantasy Star Online Blue Burst game data and published alongside
Jake's Drop Checker Lua add-on (https://github.com/jakeprobst/psodropcheckaddon).
